3. Did we avoid bubble/pill/circle defaults (8px/12px rule)?
4. Is mobile experience excellent (nav, tap targets ≥ 44px, spacing)?
5. Are animations subtle, premium, and non-distracting?
6. Is readability improved (contrast, typography, hierarchy)?

If any are "no", provide **specific revision instructions** with pixel/values where possible.

